column1: Highlights: Enables multi-gig fiber internet connections up to 2.488 Gbps downstream and 1.244 Gbps upstream.*
Supports 2.5G and 1G Ethernet UNI modes for flexible internet access.
Hot swapping feature allows quick and easy installation and application.
Supports the OMCI protocol and DDM (Digital Diagnostics Monitoring) for centralized management and real-time monitoring.
